defaultSkill level of operativesdefaultIF works are carried out by a contractor registered under a CPS then that CPS operator is expected to check and monitor the minimum technical competencies of the operator against minimum nationally recognised skills and competency levels.  The DCLG CoA 
defaultreq
defaultuires
default this measure to be documented to EN 45011 standard and accredited by UKAS within two years of initial authorisation.  As the CoA 
defaultwas
default only introduced in June 2012 existing schemes have until 6 July 2014 to satisfy this requirement.
